creator: ONESOFT
descriptionHtml:
In a near future, human conquered all planets in the Solar System, thus became the mightiest race in the Galaxy. Sensing the potential threat, all other races rallied their armed forces, bending on destroying the human race.
Humans had suffered from a sudden attack, lost many space colonies in the process. You, once a hero of classic time, was living in seclusion, now return to ride your own fighter aircraft in the battle against evil Alien Forces.
The game has classic pixel style and Danmaku barrage of bullet hell shooter.
Defend the galaxy from alien attacks, we need you!
You - Protector of the Galaxy. The Galaxy is waiting for you!
FEATURES
- Fantastic visual: Gorgeous Pixel graphics, which reminds of old school retro games, is best fitting for vertical shooters. Epic exciting sky battles are waiting for the arrival of a true hero.
- Exciting Campaign: More than 120 levels full of different challenging enemies and breathtaking action!
- Epic Boss: Wipe out swarm of minions before challenging tough and fierce big Boss battles. Taste the Danmaku barrage of bullets!
- Perfect Shoot ‘em up: Lots of fighter jets, supporting drones and gorgeous wings, ammunitions and guns, with various upgrade options to choose from, a full armory of high technologies to customize your partner!
- More additional mode: Experience more of true space battles in different modes like PvP, Endless, Tournament,… or taking part in live events for even more rewards and excitement.
- Unique PvP battles: Challenge your friends or random players through PVP battles! Fight and raise your rank to the top of the global leaderboard!
- Retro modernized: Played or didn’t play Shmup (STG) game before? No matter, this is a Super-easy control game, so easy that a tutorial is not even needed! This top-down shooter will make you feel awesome and relive the old feeling of playing scrolling game!
Lead the humanity and bring us back to our glory day again. The force is with you!
descriptionShort: Destroy evil aliens and become galaxy master with this classic shooter game!

title: Falcon Squad - Galaxy Attack

creator: ONESOFT
descriptionHtml:
The Alien shooter attacked our galaxy and put our Earth is in danger.
They destroyed all of Galactica and our Falcon Squad.
Defend the galaxy from alien attacks, and we need you!
You - Protector of the Galaxy. The Galaxy is waiting for you!
So ready your airship, equip your most potent weapon and shoot them out of your universe.

Falcon Squad: Galaxy Attack - Space Shooter is a big star of arcade shooting games like Galaga, Galaxia, Galaxian, and Galactica with the new modern combats, free fire shooter. You are going to love this most recent free galaxy shooter game.

With classic free space games genre, an old game with a new context, Galaxy Shooter - Falcon Squad puts you on fire with infinity space shooting. You will be faced with lots of aliens and deal with many evil bosses in galaxy wars. Are you sure you will survive in the battle of the alien shooter?

🚩FEATURES:
- Online shooting games, co-op with friends, gather your space team, mark your name on leader board global.
- You can also play games offline and without wifi.
- Fantastic visual: Gorgeous Pixel graphics, which reminds of old school retro games, is the best fitting for vertical shooters. Epic, exciting sky battles are waiting for the arrival of a true hero.
- Exciting Battles: More than 120 levels full of different challenging enemies and breathtaking action! Enjoy this galaxy shooter game right now.
- Epic Boss: Wipeout swarm of minions before challenging tough and fierce big Boss battles. Taste the Danmaku barrage of bullets!
- Perfect Shoot ‘em up: Lots of fighter planes, supporting drones and gorgeous wings, ammunition, and guns, with various upgrade options to choose from.
- More additional mode: Experience more of real space battles in different modes like Endless, Tournament,… or taking part in live events for even more rewards and excitement.
- Unique PvP battles: Challenge your friends or random players through PVP battles. Fight and raise your rank to the top of the global leaderboard!
- Retro modernized: Played or didn’t play Galaga, Galaxiga, Gallga game before? No matter what, this is a Super-easy control game for you. This top-down shooter will make you feel fabulous and relive the old feeling of playing scrolling game classic!

🚩HOW TO PLAY
- Slide to control your spaceship dodge enemy's bullets.
- Use coin and gem to upgrade or evolve your spaceship to fight with evil enemies and alien invaders.
- Using the power-up items, booster items to level up and defeat the alien shooter easier.

Get your ship ready for space attack in this arcade galaxy shooter game and become the space hero.

descriptionHtml:
Captain, where are you? Alien Shooters are attacking our galaxy and putting our Earth in danger. We need your help right now!

You - The protector of the Galaxy. Ready your spaceship, equip your favorite extreme weapons and shoot all the Alien Shooters out of our Galaxy.

Falcon Squad: Galaxy Attack - Space Shooter is a big star of arcade shooting games like Galaga, Galaxia, Galaxian, and Galactica with the new modern combats, free fire shooter. You are going to love this free galaxy shooter game.

With classic space games genre, an old game with a new context, Galaxy Shooter - Falcon Squad will put you on fire with infinity space shooting. You will be faced with lots of aliens and deal with many evil bosses in galaxy wars. Are you sure you will survive this battle?

🚩FEATURES:
- Online shooting games, co-op with friends, gather your space team, mark your name on the leader board global.
- You can also play games offline and without wifi.
- Classic visual: Gorgeous Pixel graphics remind you of old-school retro games and fit vertical shooters. Epic, exciting sky battles are waiting for the arrival of a true hero.
- Exciting Battles: More than 140 levels full of different challenging enemies and breathtaking action.
- Epic Boss: Wipeout a swarm of minions before challenging tough and fierce big Boss battles.
- Perfect Shoot ‘em up: Lots of spaceships, supporting drones and gorgeous wings, ammunition, and guns, with various upgrade options to choose from.
- More additional modes: Experience more real space battles in different modes like Endless, Tournament,… or taking part in live events for even more rewards, excitement, and interaction.
- Unique PvP battles: Challenge your friends or random players through PVP battles. Fight and raise your rank to the top of the global leaderboard!
- Retro modernized: Played or didn’t play Galaga, Galaxiga, Gallga game before? No matter what, this is a Super-easy control game for you. This top-down shooter game will make sure you can't take your eyes off the battles and relive the old feeling while playing the classic scrolling game!

🚩HOW TO PLAY
- Slide to control your spaceship dodge the enemy's bullets.
- Use coin and gem to upgrade or evolve your spaceship to fight evil enemies and alien invaders.
- Using the power-up items, booster items to level up and defeat the alien shooter easier.

Get your aircraft ready for the battles and become the space hero.

title: Galactic Attack - Falcon Squad

creator: ONESOFT
descriptionHtml:
Captain, where are you? Alien Shooters are attacking our galaxy and putting our Earth in danger. We need your help right now!

You - The protector of the Galaxy. Ready your spaceship, equip your favorite extreme weapons and shoot all the Alien Shooters out of our Galaxy.

Galactic Attack - Classic Shooter: Falcon Squad is a big star of arcade shooting games like Galaga, Galaxia, Galaxian, and Galactica with the new modern combats, free fire shooter. You are going to love this free galaxy shooter game.

With classic space games genre, an old game with a new context, Galactic Attack - Classic Shooter: Falcon Squad will put you on fire with infinity space shooting. You will be faced with lots of aliens and deal with many evil bosses in galaxy wars. Are you sure you will survive this battle?

🚩FEATURES:
- Online shooting games, co-op with friends, gather your space team, mark your name on the leader board global.
- You can also play games offline and without wifi.
- Classic visual: Gorgeous Pixel graphics remind you of old-school retro games and fit vertical shooters. Epic, exciting sky battles are waiting for the arrival of a true hero.
- Exciting Battles: More than 140 levels full of different challenging enemies and breathtaking action.
- Epic Boss: Wipe out a swarm of minions before challenging tough and fierce big Boss battles.
- Perfect Shoot ‘em up: Lots of spaceships, supporting drones, and gorgeous wings, ammunition, and guns, with various upgrade options to choose from.
- More additional modes: Experience more real space battles in different modes like Endless, Tournament,… or taking part in live events for even more rewards, excitement, and interaction.
- Unique PvP battles: Challenge your friends or random players through PVP battles. Fight and raise your rank to the top of the global leaderboard!
- Retro modernized: Played or didn’t play Galaga, Galaxiga, Gallga games before? No matter what, this is a Super-easy control game for you. This top-down shooter game will make sure you can't take your eyes off the battles and relive the old feeling while playing the classic scrolling game!

🚩HOW TO PLAY
- Slide to control your spaceship dodge the enemy's bullets.
- Use coin and gem to upgrade or evolve your spaceship to fight evil enemies and alien invaders.
- Using the power-up items, booster items to level up and defeat the alien shooter easier.

Get your aircraft ready for the battles and become the space hero.

title: Galactic Attack - Falcon Squad

creator: ONESOFT
descriptionHtml:
Captain, where are you? Alien Shooters are attacking our galaxy and putting our Earth in danger. We need your help right now!

You - The protector of the Galaxy. Ready your spaceship, equip your favorite extreme weapons and shoot all the Alien Shooters out of our Galaxy.

Galactic Attack - Classic Shooter: Falcon Squad is a big star of arcade shooting games like Galaga, Galaxia, Galaxian, and Galactica with the new modern combats, free fire shooter. You are going to love this free galaxy shooter game.

With classic space games genre, an old game with a new context, Galactic Attack - Classic Shooter: Falcon Squad will put you on fire with infinity space shooting. You will be faced with lots of aliens and deal with many evil bosses in galaxy wars. Are you sure you will survive this battle?

🚩FEATURES:
- Online shooting games, co-op with friends, gather your space team, mark your name on the leader board global.
- You can also play games offline and without wifi.
- Classic visual: Gorgeous Pixel graphics remind you of old-school retro games and fit vertical shooters. Epic, exciting sky battles are waiting for the arrival of a true hero.
- Exciting Battles: More than 140 levels full of different challenging enemies and breathtaking action.
- Epic Boss: Wipe out a swarm of minions before challenging tough and fierce big Boss battles.
- Perfect Shoot ‘em up: Lots of spaceships, supporting drones, and gorgeous wings, ammunition, and guns, with various upgrade options to choose from.
- More additional modes: Experience more real space battles in different modes like Endless, Tournament,… or taking part in live events for even more rewards, excitement, and interaction.
- Unique PvP battles: Challenge your friends or random players through PVP battles. Fight and raise your rank to the top of the global leaderboard!
- Retro modernized: Played or didn’t play Galaga, Galaxiga, Gallga games before? No matter what, this is a Super-easy control game for you. This top-down shooter game will make sure you can't take your eyes off the battles and relive the old feeling while playing the classic scrolling game!

🚩HOW TO PLAY
- Slide to control your spaceship dodge the enemy's bullets.
- Use coin and gem to upgrade or evolve your spaceship to fight evil enemies and alien invaders.
- Using the power-up items, booster items to level up and defeat the alien shooter easier.

Get your aircraft ready for the battles and become the space hero.

title: Galactic Attack - Falcon Squad

creator: ONESOFT
descriptionHtml:
Is your childhood, your father's childhood, associated with space fighting games like Galaga, Galaxia, Galaxian, or Galactica? Let's enjoy Falcon Squad, the contemporary version of the popular space shooter series.

A long time ago, when Alien Shooters were attacking the Galaxy and putting our earth in danger, and you were the last hope left. Let's choose the most advanced spaceship with your favorite extreme weapons and shoot all the Alien Shooters out of our Galaxy.
Don't forget to call on your teammates, fight together and against aliens and evil bosses. In the fierce battle of life and death, are you ready to become a space hero?

🚩 FEATURES:
- Unique PvP Battles: Challenge your friends or random players through PVP battles. Fight and raise your rank to the top of the global leaderboard.
- Online shooting games, co-op with friends, gather your space team.
- Play the game offline and without wifi.
- Classic Visuals: Stunning Pixel graphics remind you of old classic games with vertical shooters.
- Exciting Battles: Over 140 levels full of different challenging enemies and breathtaking action.
- Epic Boss: Destroy a horde of minions before challenging the tough and fierce Big Boss battles.
- Perfect shot: Lots of spaceships, support drones, gorgeous wings, ammunition, and guns, with various upgrade options.
- More Extra Modes: Experience more real space battles in different modes like Endless, Tournament, and more. Or join live events for more rewards, excitement, and interaction.

🚩 HOW TO PLAY:
- Slide to control your spaceship to dodge enemy bullets.
- Use coins and gems to upgrade or evolve your spaceship to fend off evil enemies and alien invaders.
- Use level up, level up items to level up and defeat the alien shooter more easily.

Enjoy the classic space shooting game. Get your aircraft ready for battle and save our Galaxy now.

title: Galactic Attack - Falcon Squad

creator: ONESOFT
descriptionHtml:
Captain, where are you? Alien Shooters are attacking our galaxy and putting our Earth in danger. We need your help right now!

You - The protector of the Galaxy. Ready your spaceship, equip your favorite extreme weapons and shoot all the Alien Shooters out of our Galaxy.

Falcon Squad: Galaxy Attack - Space Shooter is a big star of arcade shooting games like Galaga, Galaxia, Galaxian, and Galactica with the new modern combats, free fire shooter. You are going to love this classic galaxy shooter game.

With classic space games genre, an old game with a new context, Galaxy Shooter - Falcon Squad will put you on fire with infinity space shooting. You will be faced with lots of aliens and deal with many evil bosses in galaxy wars. Are you sure you will survive this battle?

🚩FEATURES:
- Online shooting games, co-op with friends, gather your space team, mark your name on the leader board global.
- You can also play games offline and without wifi.
- Classic visual: Gorgeous Pixel graphics remind you of old-school retro games and fit vertical shooters. Epic, exciting sky battles are waiting for the arrival of a true hero.
- Exciting Battles: More than 140 levels full of different challenging enemies and breathtaking action.
- Epic Boss: Wipeout a swarm of minions before challenging tough and fierce big Boss battles.
- Perfect Shoot ‘em up: Lots of spaceships, supporting drones and gorgeous wings, ammunition, and guns, with various upgrade options to choose from.
- More additional modes: Experience more real space battles in different modes like Endless, Tournament,… or taking part in live events for even more rewards, excitement, and interaction.
- Unique PvP battles: Challenge your friends or random players through PVP battles. Fight and raise your rank to the top of the global leaderboard!
- Retro modernized: Played or didn’t play Galaga, Galaxiga, Gallga game before? No matter what, this is a Super-easy control game for you. This top-down shooter game will make sure you can't take your eyes off the battles and relive the old feeling while playing the classic scrolling game!

🚩HOW TO PLAY
- Slide to control your spaceship dodge the enemy's bullets.
- Use coin and gem to upgrade or evolve your spaceship to fight evil enemies and alien invaders.
- Using the power-up items, booster items to level up and defeat the alien shooter easier.

Get your aircraft ready for the battles and become the space hero.

title: Galactic Attack - Falcon Squad

creator: ONESOFT
descriptionHtml:
Captain, where are you? Alien Shooters are attacking our galaxy and putting our Earth in danger. We need your help right now!

You - The protector of the Galaxy. Ready your spaceship, equip your favorite extreme weapons and shoot all the Alien Shooters out of our Galaxy.

Galactic Attack - Classic Shooter: Falcon Squad is a big star of arcade shooting games like Galaga, Galaxia, Galaxian, and Galactica with the new modern combats, free fire shooter. You are going to love this free galaxy shooter game.

With classic space games genre, an old game with a new context, Galactic Attack - Classic Shooter: Falcon Squad will put you on fire with infinity space shooting. You will be faced with lots of aliens and deal with many evil bosses in galaxy wars. Are you sure you will survive this battle?

🚩FEATURES:
- Online shooting games, co-op with friends, gather your space team, mark your name on the leader board global.
- You can also play games offline and without wifi.
- Classic visual: Gorgeous Pixel graphics remind you of old-school retro games and fit vertical shooters. Epic, exciting sky battles are waiting for the arrival of a true hero.
- Exciting Battles: More than 140 levels full of different challenging enemies and breathtaking action.
- Epic Boss: Wipe out a swarm of minions before challenging tough and fierce big Boss battles.
- Perfect Shoot ‘em up: Lots of spaceships, supporting drones, and gorgeous wings, ammunition, and guns, with various upgrade options to choose from.
- More additional modes: Experience more real space battles in different modes like Endless, Tournament,… or taking part in live events for even more rewards, excitement, and interaction.
- Unique PvP battles: Challenge your friends or random players through PVP battles. Fight and raise your rank to the top of the global leaderboard!
- Retro modernized: Played or didn’t play Galaga, Galaxiga, Gallga games before? No matter what, this is a Super-easy control game for you. This top-down shooter game will make sure you can't take your eyes off the battles and relive the old feeling while playing the classic scrolling game!

🚩HOW TO PLAY
- Slide to control your spaceship dodge the enemy's bullets.
- Use coin and gem to upgrade or evolve your spaceship to fight evil enemies and alien invaders.
- Using the power-up items, booster items to level up and defeat the alien shooter easier.

Get your aircraft ready for the battles and become the space hero.

VISIT US:
Galactic Attack - Classic Shooter: Falcon Squad on Facebook:
https://www.facebook.com/spacewargame/
Falcon Squad: Galaxy Attack - Space Shooter Community - Join Group to get our support quickly:
https://www.facebook.com/groups/GalaxyShooterFalconSquad/

Captain, where are you? Alien Shooters are attacking our galaxy and putting our Earth in danger. We need your help right now!

You - The protector of the Galaxy. Ready your spaceship, equip your favorite extreme weapons and shoot all the Alien Shooters out of our Galaxy.

Galactic Attack - Classic Shooter: Falcon Squad is a big star of arcade shooting games like Galaga, Galaxia, Galaxian, and Galactica with the new modern combats, free fire shooter. You are going to love this free galaxy shooter game.

With classic space games genre, an old game with a new context, Galactic Attack - Classic Shooter: Falcon Squad will put you on fire with infinity space shooting. You will be faced with lots of aliens and deal with many evil bosses in galaxy wars. Are you sure you will survive this battle?

🚩FEATURES:
- Online shooting games, co-op with friends, gather your space team, mark your name on the leader board global.
- You can also play games offline and without wifi.
- Classic visual: Gorgeous Pixel graphics remind you of old-school retro games and fit vertical shooters. Epic, exciting sky battles are waiting for the arrival of a true hero.
- Exciting Battles: More than 140 levels full of different challenging enemies and breathtaking action.
- Epic Boss: Wipe out a swarm of minions before challenging tough and fierce big Boss battles.
- Perfect Shoot ‘em up: Lots of spaceships, supporting drones, and gorgeous wings, ammunition, and guns, with various upgrade options to choose from.
- More additional modes: Experience more real space battles in different modes like Endless, Tournament,… or taking part in live events for even more rewards, excitement, and interaction.
- Unique PvP battles: Challenge your friends or random players through PVP battles. Fight and raise your rank to the top of the global leaderboard!
- Retro modernized: Played or didn’t play Galaga, Galaxiga, Gallga games before? No matter what, this is a Super-easy control game for you. This top-down shooter game will make sure you can't take your eyes off the battles and relive the old feeling while playing the classic scrolling game!

🚩HOW TO PLAY
- Slide to control your spaceship dodge the enemy's bullets.
- Use coin and gem to upgrade or evolve your spaceship to fight evil enemies and alien invaders.
- Using the power-up items, booster items to level up and defeat the alien shooter easier.

Get your aircraft ready for the battles and become the space hero.

descriptionHtml:
Falcon Squad is a big star of arcade shooting games like Galaga, Galaxia, Galaxian, and Galactica with the new modern combats, free fire shooter. You are going to love this free galaxy shooter game.

With classic space games genre, an old game with a new context, Falcon Squad will put you on fire with infinity space shooting. You will be faced with lots of aliens and deal with many evil bosses in galaxy wars. Are you sure you will survive this battle?

🚩FEATURES:
- Classic visual: Gorgeous Pixel graphics remind you of old-school retro games and fit vertical shooters. This top-down shooter game makes sure you can't take your eyes off the battles and relive the old feeling while playing the classic scrolling game!
- Build your squadron with the massive hangar full of spaceships, supporting drones and gorgeous wings, and add-on gadgets with numerous customization.
- Hundreds of challenging and breathtaking levels.
- Real-time battles: Challenge your friends or random players through real-time battle modes such as PvP, 2vs2, and Tournament. Fight and raise your rank to the top of the global leaderboard.
- Clan: Like-minded players progress and fight together, building their community to take down tougher opponents.
- Reward system: Play every day to earn free prizes and tons of free stuff! Complete daily missions and upgrade your squad!
- Additional modes: Experience further in different modes like Endless, Trial, Boss Assault,… and take part in live events for even more rewards.
- Online and offline game modes.

🚩HOW TO PLAY:
- Slide to control your spaceship and dodge the enemy's bullets.
- Use gold and gem to upgrade or evolve your spaceship to fight evil enemies and alien invaders.
- Use the active skill of spaceship and wing and collect power-up items to enhance your whole power.

Get your aircraft ready for the battles and become the space hero.

VISIT US:

Falcon Squad is a big star of arcade shooting games like Galaga, Galaxia, Galaxian, and Galactica with the new modern combats, free fire shooter. You are going to love this free galaxy shooter game.

With classic space games genre, an old game with a new context, Falcon Squad will put you on fire with infinity space shooting. You will be faced with lots of aliens and deal with many evil bosses in galaxy wars. Are you sure you will survive this battle?

🚩FEATURES:
- Classic visual: Gorgeous Pixel graphics remind you of old-school retro games and fit vertical shooters. This top-down shooter game makes sure you can't take your eyes off the battles and relive the old feeling while playing the classic scrolling game!
- Build your squadron with the massive hangar full of spaceships, supporting drones and gorgeous wings, and add-on gadgets with numerous customization.
- Hundreds of challenging and breathtaking levels.
- Real-time battles: Challenge your friends or random players through real-time battle modes such as PvP, 2vs2, and Tournament. Fight and raise your rank to the top of the global leaderboard.
- Clan: Like-minded players progress and fight together, building their community to take down tougher opponents.
- Reward system: Play every day to earn free prizes and tons of free stuff! Complete daily missions and upgrade your squad!
- Additional modes: Experience further in different modes like Endless, Trial, Boss Assault,… and take part in live events for even more rewards.
- Online and offline game modes.

🚩HOW TO PLAY:
- Slide to control your spaceship and dodge the enemy's bullets.
- Use gold and gem to upgrade or evolve your spaceship to fight evil enemies and alien invaders.
- Use the active skill of spaceship and wing and collect power-up items to enhance your whole power.

Get your aircraft ready for the battles and become the space hero.

title:
Falcon Squad
100.11

container.value: 470 North Bridge Road, #05-12 Bugis Cube, Singapore 188735

creator: 1SOFT
descriptionHtml:
Are you ready to save the galaxy? Join Falcon Squad and defend humanity from a dangerous alien invasion! Inspired by classic arcade games like 1945 Air Force and Galaxy Attack, this space shooter will take you through epic battles against enemies from the depths of space. Enjoy Pixel graphics that evoke retro gaming while fighting to save the universe.

### 🚀 FIGHT OFF THE SPACE INVADERS
In Falcon Squad, you'll explore the vastness of space and face dangerous alien invaders in breathtaking battles. Take part in the galaxy attack and defeat the most powerful enemies. Show your skills and become the hero who will save the galaxy!

### 💥 CREATE A CLAN AND FIGHT TOGETHER
Form or join a clan to battle alongside other players with the same goals. Defeat the strongest enemies, earn special rewards, and advance faster with your team’s help. With your clan, you can dominate the space battlefield and win together!

### 🌠 UPGRADE YOUR PLANE AND PROTECT THE GALAXY
As you progress through the levels, you'll face increasingly powerful enemies. Upgrade your spaceship with stronger weapons, more durable shields, and faster boosters to destroy the alien invaders. Only the best pilots can save the galaxy in this shooting game.

### 🏆 REAL-TIME PVP BATTLES AND COMPETITION
Challenge your friends or players from all over the world in real-time PvP battles. Take part in 2vs2 skirmishes or tournaments to climb to the top of the global leaderboard. Become the top pilot of Falcon Squad and leave your mark in space!

### 🛸 FACE THE MIGHTIEST BOSSES
Battle against the mightiest bosses in the galaxy and use all your skills to defeat them. In this alien shooter, strategy and quick reflexes are the key to victory. Prove that you’re a true hero in the boss battles!

### 🎮 GAME FEATURES:
- 🎨 Pixel graphics that bring back the spirit of retro arcade games
- 👾 An arcade shooter inspired by classics like 1945 Air Force and Galaxy Attack
- ⚔️ Real-time PvP, 2vs2 battles, and tournaments
- 🚀 Upgrade your plane and face stronger enemies at each level
- 🏅 Daily missions, clan wars, and special events
- 💀 Face the galaxy’s most powerful bosses and win great rewards

Are you ready to save the galaxy? Join Falcon Squad and take part in epic space battles to defeat the invaders! This space shooter is perfect for you. Play now and conquer the galaxy! 🚀
